Player should be able to ...
    create an account
    sign in
    create a character
    select a character
    remove a character

Characters should be able to ...
    add a kill for the day
    add kills of the day to total kills
    select if character gets 10% XP bonus for high stats
    calculate XP gained for the day
    calculate Fighter specific XP for kills
    remove a kill for the day because of error

Kill lists should be able to ...
    add creatures to list
    remove creatures from list

Creatures should include ...
    Creature name
    XP per hit die
    number of hit die
